item.dc:creator: @heroisgay heroisgay
item.description:
@heroisgay wrote:

strengthpk:

log in teleport to where you want to change it… do ::pos gets the coords… and then go to client.java ctrl f and type those coords… and then find the coords you want it to bring you to and change it to that.

You practically said what stormcutter said only you said it as if the commands on his server were the exact same as your own.
